en_97969_0	Kilinochchi troops extended their assistance for conduct of the annual Kovil Pooja at Kanakambigai Amman Hindu Kovil on Friday (19).
en_97969_1	Troops at the Security Force Headquarters offered refreshments to the devotees.
en_97969_2	On the instructions of the Commander, Security Forces - Kilinochchi, Major General Vijitha Ravipriya, troops offered refreshments to the Hindu devotees who were participating in the Pooja ceremony.
en_97969_3	More than 1000 devotees, attending the final segment of the ceremony received this Army hospitality.
